{"tid":200713,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）WIN7detect唔到PS4手掣","createTime":"2017-04-14T07:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T15:30:15.000Z","uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26745f9760add978c19bc552981b5681006d2735","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"小弟之前係steam買咗dark souls, 幾個月前用ps4手掣連落win7到玩都好順利<br />\n<br />\n近日因為佢dlc出咗所以想開返隻ds3嚟玩, 點知發現個部電腦detect唔到個手掣嘅存在, 搞到玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係「裝置和印表機」到搵唔到有手掣的存在... (明明以前會有)<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZSs1WO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZSs1WO.jpg&h=f1b877a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前會係咁 (上網搵的example)<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mp4cn.com/d/file/mrzixun/peishi/2012-07-25/7d859732bb0dd574cd0c3cde57ac53cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mp4cn.com%2Fd%2Ffile%2Fmrzixun%2Fpeishi%2F2012-07-25%2F7d859732bb0dd574cd0c3cde57ac53cc.jpg&h=e7891585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網搵咗好耐都搵唔到解決方法, 我覺得係少咗個驅動程式, 但又唔知少咗d咩, 同埋去邊到down返<br />\n<br />\n睇裝置管理員又冇咗舊「遊戲控制器」的驅動程式<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4SP6yz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4SP6yz1.jpg&h=89964b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇用, 但都試過裝埋呢舊野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5n0ua1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5n0ua1.jpg&h=218f9604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我又以為係個手掣有問題, 但係連返落ps4到又好順暢完全冇事<br />\n一連落電腦到就冇反應, 但係後面會著橙燈顯示係連到+差緊電<br />\n所以我覺得應該係我部電腦有問題, 但係我唔知可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 求全能的連登大神幫幫手"},{"pid":"d4261e2eeb2493e5a0b765d3bc58b089ddb4be73","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ece2b0869cc92b6f571a261d88f2bbe3656ec4","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7eb06c943f46e8ca50e2800f6a702b7aa8b7c8","tid":200713,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:22:04.000Z","msg":"用xbox囉"},{"pid":"0bbd5d643a6e7920f6407832c5d3472de610dd42","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用xbox囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係解決唔到我就去買過個xbox手掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗住既然有個ps4手掣可以用就唔洗再曬錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d699e430c265c991b1fb84d714c30d72ddb13d90","tid":200713,"uid":32197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:48:09.000Z","msg":"用DS4 Tools 可以google下教學<br />\nWin7冇Win10 咁煩"},{"pid":"ae5191ce80ca40ab6d5471c2376f357a02f097e4","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"我最後都係買咗個Xbox one手掣, 仲將win7升咗上win10, 都係用唔到...<br />\n<br />\n部電腦根本search唔到手掣嘅裝置, 可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rqw9v9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqw9v9y.jpg&h=3d960ae6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4907cb0230246e0392e8fa3da1fc463f155a81c5","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3215141cc6dfd0528340be5875057ce27f383f52","tid":200713,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"攪咁多飛機<br />\nPs4制+佢條usb線吉落電腦用得啦"},{"pid":"9a24b0128d237906f734e693dcf0d6e0708017c5","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攪咁多飛機<br />\nPs4制+佢條usb線吉落電腦用得啦</blockquote><br />\n我半年前都係咁就用到<br />\n但係依家唔知做乜就突然用唔到<br />\n如果用到我就唔洗搞咁多飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw thanks"},{"pid":"1c4cc74ca798a0f4a7c60768be2636f78d36d60f","tid":200713,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>攪咁多飛機<br />\nPs4制+佢條usb線吉落電腦用得啦</blockquote><br />\n我半年前都係咁就用到<br />\n但係依家唔知做乜就突然用唔到<br />\n如果用到我就唔洗搞咁多飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw thanks</blockquote><br />\n手制係唔係有RESET架?<br />\n係就禁住幾秒先再隊落USB試試"},{"pid":"fe18b1863ec9c51857ca0431326f809ab8390aaf","tid":200713,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:30:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>攪咁多飛機<br />\nPs4制+佢條usb線吉落電腦用得啦</blockquote><br />\n我半年前都係咁就用到<br />\n但係依家唔知做乜就突然用唔到<br />\n如果用到我就唔洗搞咁多飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw thanks</blockquote><br />\n手制係唔係有RESET架?<br />\n係就禁住幾秒先再隊落USB試試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nps4個reset制係for佢Detect ps4果陣reset, 試過照試下禁完先隊落usb都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nxbox手掣就今日先新買唔知點reset... 不過禁得嘅制都禁過曬, 都係冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}